    "rationale": "The CFD hemolysis model meets all seven assessed credibility factors at or above required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with medium model influence. The High assurance level reflects the regulatory submission context and the breadth of validation evidence across the COU operating envelope. All primary QoIs demonstrate agreement within pre-specified acceptance thresholds against FDA experimental data. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
